<section id="stock-list" class="stock-list" aria-label="ストック一覧">
  <div id="stock-loading" class="loading-container">
    <div class="loading-spinner" role="status" aria-label="読み込み中">
      <span class="sr-only">読み込み中...</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="stock-empty" class="empty-state" hidden>
    <h2 class="empty-state-heading">まだスライドがありません</h2>
    <p>以下のサービスからお気に入りのスライドを見つけて追加してみましょう。</p>

    <div class="empty-state-providers">
      <a href="https://speakerdeck.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="empty-state-provider-link badge-speakerdeck">
        SpeakerDeck <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.docswell.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="empty-state-provider-link badge-docswell">
        Docswell <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="empty-state-provider-link badge-google_slides">
        Google Slides <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="empty-state-action">
      <span aria-hidden="true">↑</span> 上のフォームにスライドの URL を貼り付けて「追加」ボタンを押すだけ！
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<div id="load-more-container" hidden>
  <button id="load-more-btn" type="button" class="btn-secondary">
    もっと読み込む
  </button>
</div>
